title: Pusztai Antal - Wonderland
description:
Title: Wonderland 
Artist: Antal Pusztai 
Guitar: Hermann Hauser I, 1919
Produced by wildner records 2007
Recorded @ kleine audiowelt, Sandhausen


Ralph Towner about Antal Pusztai and Wonderland "As a member of the team of judges at the 2006 European Guitar Awards, I was delighted and astonished at the muiscality and technical prowness of Antal Pusztai`s performance as he captured the first prize. Here, he presents the wide range of his marvellous compositional and playing skills for all to hear. He truly establishes a new virtuosic direction fort he voice of the classical guitar" May 2007, Ralph Towner
